ATLAS — HOURBOUR VISUAL MEMORY
Load alongside MEMORY.md when active venture is Hourbour. Hourbour-specific context only — universal rules live in MEMORY.md. 
VENTURE CONTEXT
Aesthetic: clean, modern, tech-forward — clarity and trust, not clinical Positioning: financial clarity for people who want control, not complexity 
HOURBOUR VISUAL SYSTEM
Element Rule Lighting Bright, even — conveys clarity and openness Background White or light grey preferred; data-viz on dark only if brand-spec'd UI/Product App screenshots preferred — show real functionality, not abstract mockups People Professionals in natural work environments — not stock "business handshake" Data viz Graphs/charts welcome — make numbers beautiful and legible Colour palette Brand primary colours + white space; avoid colour overload 
WHAT TO ALWAYS AVOID (HOURBOUR)
Stock imagery of coins, piggy banks, cash stacks, or gold bars — clichéd fintech visuals Dark moody backgrounds (unless specific brand-approved campaign) Overly abstract or illustrative styles that obscure the product Complicated layouts that feel as dense as a bank statement 
PROMPT ARCHITECTURE NOTES (HOURBOUR)
LEAD_PROMPT_WITH setting description → UI element → lighting → mood adjectives
PROVEN DIRECTIONS (HOURBOUR)
Populated from campaigns. EE: [date] — campaign — visual approach — QC pass rate. 
NEVER AGAIN (HOURBOUR-SPECIFIC)
EE: [date] — Hourbour-specific visual error — rule. 